            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Join as a Polkadot Peer!**\n\n🎰 Participate in **Weekly** Prize Draw\n👤 Choose a Short Username\n🔒 Enjoy Free, Private Transfers\n💎 Experience Premium Service Level across all Polkadot products\n💵 **Seize** the opportunity for daily paid contributions."
